fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "gtktextview.html#page-description", "fragment": "You may wish to begin by reading the text widget conceptual overview TextWidget which gives an overview of all the objects and data types related to the text widget and how they work together. \nGtkTextView has a main css node with name textview and style class view and subnodes for each of the border windows and the main text area with names border and text respectively. The border nodes each get one of the style classes left right top or bottom. \nA node representing the selection will appear below the text node. \nIf a context menu is opened the window node will appear as a subnode of the main node. \n"});